title: 147: The Target Haul Episode (June '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode (June '21 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey are taste-testing some amazing new finds like a plant-based breakfast-patty sandwich, jackfruit crumbles that will blow you away, chicken skewers, pizza-flavored dip, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of the episode, a cauliflower pizza bowl that is OUT OF THIS WORLD! Are you ready? Push play now, and then when it’s all over, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We really hit the bullseye this week with our best Target Haul ever!
